Package: renv2binder
Title: Converts renv lockfiles to binder friendly formats
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ted", "Laderas",email="tladera2@fredhutch.org", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: |
    Renv is a powerful tool for package management, but it is not compatible with tools such as binder, which need either an install.R or DESCRIPTION file to be generated to install the correct packages.
